name: Queen Medb (Fate Grand Order)
description:
Lora model of Medb from Fate Grand Order. Preview images were made with weight 0.7-1. This one actually requires some tinkering with weight and images without highres often show obvious quality drop so highres recommended.

It's been a while since I made model with this many outfits but I'm happy in general how this worked out. I had some versions of this model that worked more consistentently with default weight and seemed more flexible, but had problems retaining details and in the end I feel this version is a good sweet spot.

  • First ascension - medb \(fate\), tiara, fur coat, armor, white elbow gloves, white skirt, white thigh boots. You can try adding open coat to negatives since that's how I intended to get the fully-covered-up look, but I didn't managed to get it to work as well as some fanarts. If you figure out good prompt for that, let me know.

  • Second ascension - medb \(fate\), tiara, armor, white elbow gloves, white skirt, white boots

  • Third ascension - medb \(fate\), tiara, white bra, midriff, white elbow gloves, white skirt, white boots

  • Warden outfit - medb \(fate\), peaked cap, hair bun, red bra, red elbow gloves, midriff, red skirt, red thigh boots. I feel lower weight of about 0.8 helps here.

  • Full warden uniform (with jacket) - medb \(fate\), peaked cap, hair bun, military uniform, white gloves, black skirt, red thigh boots.

  • Grail Live event outfit (white dress) - medb (fate), white hairband, bare shoulders, white dress, sandals. This one have simplier tiara so it helps to add regular tiara to negatives for more accurate look.

  • First bikini - medb \(fate\), side ponytail, mini crown, goggles on head, goggles, pink bikini, sandals. I'm surprised how well this one comes out considering that I only had 3 images, but you do have to dial down the weight to around 0.7. Due to flip augmentation sometimes does twintails.

  • Second bikini - medb \(fate\), tiara, ribbon choker, twintails, black bikini, gold bracelet, sandals. Bikini color is full black about half the time sadly.

  • Third bikini - medb \(fate\), white headwear, pom pom \(clothes\), white bikini, white wristband, uneven legwear. This outfit probably works worst of all.

  • Knocknarea - medb \(fate\), simple tiara, frilled collar, black bodysuit, black high heels. Best to add regular tiara to negatives because the one used here is different. You can optionally try fur scarf - results may vary.
